sent.orig: A suicide attempt is a deliberate attempt by a person to end their own life.
sent.trans: 自杀是一个人有意结束自己生命的行为。

sent.orig: He was foiled in his attempt to deceive us/His attempt to deceive us was foiled.
sent.trans: 他企图欺骗我们，但没有得逞。

sent.orig: Comrade Lei attempt to trap satellites, set a grbordermother organization to attempt of us.
sent.trans: 雷锋同志把他的一切都献给了人民，给咱们大部份人树立了唯一的好榜样。

sent.orig: For more than two weeks, she made attempt after attempt-to no avail.
sent.trans: 超过二个星期，她做了企图在企图以后-无益。

sent.orig: The end: The majority of people attempt suicide repeat that attempt until they succeed.
sent.trans: 大部分要自杀的人，都会重复尝试，直到成功。
